WEBVTT

00:00.006 --> 00:00.008
-

00:00.106 --> 00:02.206
<i>Previously on Avengers...</i>

00:02.507 --> 00:06.576
Only those worthy
of the thunder may wield Mjolnir, villain.

00:06.611 --> 00:08.812
By using the last Norn stone
you risk breaking down

00:08.846 --> 00:11.448
the walls to Muspelheim itself.

00:11.482 --> 00:15.685
This stone can protect me from
your magic. That's all that matters.

00:15.720 --> 00:19.623
The Twilight sword is gone.
The barriers to Muspelheim have fallen.

00:19.657 --> 00:21.791
Surtur has returned.

00:21.826 --> 00:27.531
<i>Amora The Enchantress,
you serve me now.</i>

00:30.834 --> 00:33.834
<b>2x08 - The Ballad of Beta Ray Bill</b>

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
